This paper focuses on designing a pricing mechanism for demand response in multi-tenant data centers, which involves aspects of data center management (cs.DC), game theory (cs.GT), and mechanism design (cs.CE). The paper also discusses simulation studies to evaluate the proposed mechanism, which falls under software engineering (cs.SE) and control systems (cs.SY).
